* ''[[In the Shadow of the Moon]]'' (2007)
* ''[[When We Left Earth: The NASA Missions]] (miniseries) (2008)
* ''[[James May on the Moon]] (documentary commemorating 40 years since the landings) (2009)
* ''[[NASA's Story]]''

