*Bulfinch, Thomas (1834). ''Bulfinch's Mythology.'' New York: Harper &amp; Row, 1970, p.&amp;nbsp;348. ISBN 0-690-57260-3.
*Marshall Jones Company (1930). ''Mythology of All Races'' Series, Volume 2 ''Eddic'', Great Britain: Marshall Jones Company, 1930, pp.&amp;nbsp;220–221.

