===Current===
* [[Mike Rann]] – [[Premiers of South Australia|Premier of South Australia]] since [[South Australian state election, 2002|6 March 2002]]
* [[Anna Bligh]] – [[Premiers of Queensland|Premier of Queensland]] since 13 September 2007 (first female premier of Queensland)
* [[Paul Henderson (Australian politician)|Paul Henderson]] – [[Chief Minister of the Northern Territory]] since 26 November 2007
* [[Eric Ripper]] – [[Leader of the Opposition (Western Australia)|Leader of the Opposition of Western Australia]] since 23 September 2008
* [[Daniel Andrews]] – [[Leader of the Opposition (Victoria)|Leader of the Opposition of Victoria]] since 3 December 2010
* [[Lara Giddings]] – [[Premier of Tasmania]] since 24 January 2011 (first female premier of Tasmania)
* [[John Robertson]] – [[Leader of the Opposition (New South Wales)|Leader of the Opposition of New South Wales]] since 31 March 2011
* [[Katy Gallagher]] – [[Chief Minister of the Australian Capital Territory]] since 16 May 2011

