      <comment>Undid revision 422299377 by [[Special:Contributions/196.20.164.227|196.20.164.227]] ([[User talk:196.20.164.227|talk]])Info on actual dodo bird not appropriate for article on character from Alice in Wonderland.</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox character
| name        = Dodo
| series      =
| image       = [[Image:De Alice's Abenteuer im Wunderland Carroll pic 10.jpg|250px|]]
| caption     = [[John Tenniel]]'s illustration of the Dodo in &quot;A Caucus-Race and a Long Tale&quot;. An illustration from Alice in Wonderland.
